summary: An ordinance canceling the payment of the 2nd installation on lots 8 to 10, block 13, Latona 1st Addition to the City of Seattle, assessed for the improvement of North Lake Avenue, et al, in Local Improvement District No. 1097, authorized by Ordinance No. 12496, amounting to $4.34, which was paid in error by Walter McNett of Ottumwa, Iowa, as evidenced by Treasurer's receipt No. S9819; authorizing the City Treasurer to accept payment of the above amount on lots 8 and 9, in block 13, Latona Addition (which are assessed for the same improvement) as of January 18, 1909, and to reinstate the original assessment against lots 8 to 10, inclusive, block 13, Latona First Addition.
